    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, making it an ideal choice for a buyer who needs a dependable mode of transportation and isn't concerned with a perfect exterior. The body shows its age with various scratches, a few small dings, and some clear coat peeling on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and a few minor stains, but the cabin remains comfortable. Mechanically, it starts right up and runs well, though it may require some routine maintenance items in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done.",
