    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable ride that's ready for its next adventure? This vehicle is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity to own a reliable car at a great price! While it shows some honest character and wear from its time on the road, it remains a solid choice for anyone needing a practical daily driver. Come see how this well-traveled vehicle can fit into your life!",
