    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, having been fastidiously maintained by a single owner and stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely no chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in an 'as-new' state; the premium leather upholstery shows zero signs of wear on the bolsters, and every electronic component functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a comprehensive service history exclusively through authorized dealerships. Recently fitted with a fresh set of high-performance tires and having just completed its major interval service, this car requires nothing but a driver who appreciates mechanical and aesthetic perfection. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
